  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time collaborative trip planning via WebSocket",
    "Interactive Leaflet maps with photo markers, clustering, and route optimization",
    "Budget tracking with multi-currency support and per-person/per-day splitting",
    "Packing lists with templates, bag tracking, and user assignment",
    "Reservations and bookings for flights, hotels, restaurants, and more",
    "Progressive Web App (PWA) with offline support via Workbox",
    "Single Sign-On (OIDC) with Google, Apple, Keycloak, Authentik, and more",
    "Two-Factor Authentication (TOTP/MFA)",
    "MCP server for AI assistant integration (Claude, Cursor, etc.)",
    "Multilingual support (8 languages including RTL Arabic)",
    "Admin panel with user management, invite links, and auto-backups",
    "Atlas addon: interactive visited-countries world map with stats",
    "Vacay addon: personal vacation day planner with public holiday support",
    "PDF export of complete trip plans",
    "Helm chart for Kubernetes deployment"
  ],
